            <p class="content-txt">
              We broke the campaign creation to multiple steps making it easier to
              configure the settings of the campaign.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="features">
          <div class="container flex">
            <div class="features__content" data-aos="fade-up">
              <h2 class="content-head">Extensive Journey builder</h2>
              <p class="content-txt">
                Journey builder is the core of the product, it is used to create
                custom user journeys and configure marketing activites accordingly.
                We have introduced multiple features into journey builder to keep it
                intuitive and easier.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="features__tags">
              <span>NEW FEATURES</span>
