                  We restructured settings to be intutive and self served so that
                  users can setup and configure the product to their needs. We
                  introduced help-bites; small block of text guiding users about the
                  module
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="services__list_item">
              <div class="services__list_item-content" data-aos="fade-up">
                <h2 class="content-head">Reduced information overload</h2>
